ide."},{"content":"Preheat oven to 200°C."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Spaghetti"},{"content":"Place Parmesan cheese and bread in mixing bowl then grate <strong><b>10 sec\/speed 10<b><\/strong>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside."},{"content":"Remove semi-frozen chicken meat from freezer, place in mixing bowl and chop <strong><b>10 sec\/speed 6<b><\/strong>."},{"content":"Add milk, grated Parmesan-bread mixture, oregano, salt, black pepper and egg then mix <strong><b>10 sec\/speed 5<b><\/strong>. Transfer to a bowl, shape with oiled hands 16 meatballs (approx. Ø 4 cm) and arrange them in the casserole dish with tomato sauce. Bake for 20-30 minutes (200°C). Meanwhile clean mixing bowl and prepare the spaghetti."}],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","1h","4 portions"]}